Note on dataset content: The image files in `catalog/images/` are manufacturer
press-kit photography sourced from each automaker's official media site or
public CDN. Copyright in those images remains with the respective manufacturer.
They are included here under fair-use editorial / portfolio-demonstration
context. Anyone forking or redistributing this repository for purposes beyond
personal study should review the source manufacturers' image-use terms
independently. The MIT license above applies to the catalog code, schema,
JSON dataset structure, and original prose — not to third-party image content.
